title: North Hunterdon soccer's Heather Tostevin talks after overtime goal against Belvidere (VIDEO)
text:
Complete Box Score Â» 
After many shots and chances throughout the game for North Hunterdon , senior midfielder Heather Tostevin finally delivered a Hunterdon/Warren/Sussex quarterfinal win for the Lions on Saturday. 
She scored with 4:56 left in the first overtime give North Hunterdon a 1-0 road win over Belvidere . 
See what the senior had to say after her big goal in the video at the top of this post.
